---
// Featured testimonial from RJ GO
---

<section class="featured-testimonial-section py-16 bg-[#0d0f1a]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="inline-block bg-[#f0622a] text-white px-4 md:px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide mb-3 md:mb-4">
        CLIENT SUCCESS
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4 leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 800;">
        Real Results from <span class="text-[#f0622a]">Real Businesses</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-[#131627] rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-12 shadow-xl border border-[rgba(240,98,42,0.15)]">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
          <div class="flex gap-1.5 md:gap-2 text-yellow-400 text-xl md:text-2xl">
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          </div>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="text-base md:text-2xl text-[#e8eaf2] text-center leading-relaxed mb-6 md:mb-8 font-medium italic">
          "I am very happy with the results from BrightForge! My site gets more visitors and my business is growing. They explain things clearly and make the process easy. Great service all around."
        </blockquote>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 md:gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#f0622a] to-[#ff9a62] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg md:text-2xl">
            R
          </div>
          <div class="text-left">
            <h4 class="text-base md:text-xl font-bold text-[#e8eaf2]">
              <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110455532132624140129/reviews?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-[#f0622a] transition-colors">
                RJ GO
              </a>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-[#f0622a] font-medium text-sm md:text-base">Google Review • Jun 20, 2022</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
